1.) Raspberry Pi 3 Model B or above 

2.) Bread Board

3.) PIR motion sensor

4.) Photoresistor or LDR sensor

5.) 10k ohm and 220 ohm Resistors

6.) Jumper wires(M to M, M to F, F to F)

7.) Small Led's

8.) Power adaptor 

9.) Arduino UNO R3

10.) Arduino Cable

11.) SD card(with Raspbian OS installed)
